%%{init: {"theme":"neutral"}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Draft : draft()

    Draft --> Active : sign()<br/>[start_date &lt;= today]
    Draft --> Cancelled : voidBeforeStart()

    Active --> Suspended : suspend()<br/>(congé sans solde, etc.)
    Suspended --> Active : resume()

    Active --> Renewed : renew()<br/>[end_date approche]
    Renewed --> Active

    Active --> Expired : reach(end_date)
    Active --> Terminated : terminate()<br/>(rupture anticipée)

    Expired --> [*]
    Terminated --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]

    note right of Active
      Contrat « courant » :
      end_date IS NULL
      OU end_date &gt;= today
    end note
